prodNameC: "西門子" N血清澱粉樣蛋白A乳膠試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
N SAA Reagent consists of lyophilized polystyrene particles coated with sheep antibodies to human SAA. 
N SAA Standard SY (human) is produced from human serum with elevated levels of SAA.
N SAA Control SY (human) is produced from human serum with eelevated levels of SAA. 
N SAA Supplementary Reagent consists of a glycine NaCl buffer solution containing pyrrolidone and detergent as additives.

efficacy: 利用顆粒增效免疫比濁原理對人類血清或肝素化血漿中的血清澱粉樣蛋白A(SAA)。
